idget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<table style=\"max-width: 600px;\"><tbody><tr style=\"background-color: #193556; color: white;\"><td width=\"258\"><strong><em>\u00a0<\/em><\/strong><\/td><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Timing<\/strong><\/td><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Fluid Density<\/strong><\/td><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Wall<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td width=\"258\"><em>Acute Pancreatic Fluid Collection<\/em><\/td><td width=\"99\">\u2264 4 Weeks<\/td><td width=\"124\">Homogenous<\/td><td width=\"114\">No Defined<\/td><\/tr><tr><td width=\"258\"><em>Pancreatic Pseudocyst<\/em><\/td><td width=\"99\">&gt; 4 Weeks<\/td><td width=\"124\">Homogenous<\/td><td width=\"114\">Well Defined<\/td><\/tr><tr><td width=\"258\"><em>Acute Necrotic Collection<\/em><\/td><td width=\"99\">\u2264 4 Weeks<\/td><td width=\"124\">Heterogenous<\/td><td width=\"114\">No Defined<\/td><\/tr><tr><td width=\"258\"><em>Walled-Off Pancreatic Necrosis<\/em><\/td><td width=\"99\">&gt; 4 Weeks<\/td><td width=\"124\">Heterogenous<\/td><td width=\"114\">Well Defined<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-ce47d33 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"ce47d33\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-6842708\" data-id=\"6842708\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-adaf7b8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"adaf7b8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<ul><li>Term \u201cPancreatic Abscess\u201d No Longer Used<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-bd16086 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"bd16086\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-57675e9\" data-id=\"57675e9\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b025d2b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b025d2b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Diagnosis<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Diagnosis Requires \u2265 2 Of:<ul><li>Acute Persistent Severe Epigastric Pain<\/li><li>Elevated Lipase\/Amylase \u2265 3x Normal<\/li><li>CT Characteristic<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Severity Classification<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><em>Mild<\/em>: No Local\/Systemic Complications or Organ Failure<\/li><li><em>Moderate<\/em>: Local\/Systemic Complications or Organ Failure &lt; 48 Hours<\/li><li><em>Severe<\/em>: Persistent Organ Failure &gt; 48 Hours<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Treatment<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Initial Treatment: Medical (Aggressive IV Fluids &amp; NPO)<\/li><li>Considerations:<ul><li>Early Refeeding (\u2264 48 Hours) if Stable &amp; Tolerating Diet<ul><li>If Not Tolerating Oral Diet: Give Enteral Nutrition Through Jejunal Feeding Tube<\/li><li>*Old Dogma to Give TPN and Avoid Enteral Nutrition Disproven \u2013 Increased Mortality<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Give ABX Only if There is Concern for Infection<ul><li>*Prophylactic ABX Are Not Recommended Regardless of Severity or Necrosis<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Gallstone Pancreatitis:<ul><li><strong>25-30% Risk of Recurrence <\/strong>within 6-18 Weeks<\/li><li>All Should Undergo <strong>Elective Cholecystectomy During the Same Admission<\/strong><ul><li><strong>Mild-Moderate<\/strong> Pancreatitis: <strong>Early <\/strong>(&lt; 48 Hours)<strong> OK<\/strong><\/li><li>Severe Pancreatitis: Wait Until Resolved<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Cholangitis or Signs of Clear Obstruction: <strong>ERCP<\/strong> &amp; Sphincterotomy<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-6ec69b1\" data-id=\"6ec69b1\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5657531 elementor-widget elementor-widget-t